summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the permit granted to the Fremont Dock Company to use and occupy that portion of Fremont Avenue North under the Fremont Bridge lying north of the Lake Washington Ship Canal by amending Section 1 and 13 Ordinance 106488 to establish the annual fee for the last five (5) years of the permit, and granting to the City of Seattle a twenty-five (25) foot wide easement across Permittee's property.
